definition:
Someone descended from Heber who was a man of the tribe of Asher living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at Gen.46.17; 
 son of: Beriah (H1283); 
 brother of: Malchiel (H4439); 
 father of: Japhlet (H3310), Shomer (H7763H), Hotham (H2369) and Shua (H7774)
Group of che.ver (חֶ֫בֶר "Heber" H2268) 
